    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tags, tickets, or labels attached to an item for sale, to show its price. The tag may be attached to the item with a cord or string, or it may be attached to the item by an adhesive backing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
